{{Quote|What separates the Swordmasters from so many of the other groups is that they ''deserve'' attention, especially by the Alliance.|[[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Tura Raftican]], [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]].|<ref name="air" />}}
The '''Zulirian Swordmasters''' were a group of blade wielding sword collectors who were founded on the planet [[Zuliria]] by [[Ther-das]]. As time went on, the group members discovered that they were gifted 'swordsmen' and combatants. Less than one year after being founded, they altered their original mission from 'collecting' to using their knowledge to become vigilantes and began showing a trend of attacking unarmed enemies.<ref name="air" />

In [[Teloc Ol-sen]], the Swordmasters met a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] cell, with one of the Rebels using a [[Vibroblade/Legends|vibroblade]]. Zulirian Swordmaster [[Kaltor Naklian]] challenged this Rebel to a duel and, when he refused, Naklian simply [[Death/Legends|killed]] him. The Rebels tried to counter attack, but the Swordmasters massacred them. They were then considered a threat to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]], receiving reports written by [[Tura Raftican]] and other Rebels.<ref name="air" />

